    <item>
      <title>日元等待日本央行关注，美元持稳</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/yen-bides-time-with-boj-focus-dollar-steady-2024-01-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在日本央行(BOJ)做出备受关注的政策决定之前，日元周二徘徊在两个月低点附近，预计日本央行将维持其超宽松的货币政策环境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/yen-bides-time-with-boj-focus-dollar-steady-2024-01-23/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 00:59:58 GMT</pubDate>
